[Warehouse electricity consumption
in Longxing in week 1, 2024]

74
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,920
I've checked this warehouse before.

75
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,056
Convenient transportation

76
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,080
and high rental rates.

77
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,920
So the power bill's a bit higher.

78
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,696
After I noticed you were acting strange,

79
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,120
I quietly followed you here.

80
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,800
If I hadn't come today,

81
