keep me in the dark all along?

82
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,680
Song Pa is ruthless.

83
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,960
Jiang Meng is craftier than a fox.

84
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,560
Bringing you along
will only add more risk.

85
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,040
Honestly, I didn't expect

86
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,320
