in the act.

87
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,200
And yet he still managed to slip away.

88
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,240
Catching Jiang Meng isn't that easy.

89
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,440
And now isn't the best time anyway.

90
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,896
Better to let them
mess themselves up first.

91
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,200
Eventually, they'll show a flaw.

92
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,056
That way we can figure out

93
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,680
