94
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,880
Turns out you only
threw a stone into the lake today.

95
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:04,280
But after this, they'll be wary of you.

96
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,640
There's no fighting crooks
without danger.

97
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,976
It's just that Song Pa now knows
we're working together.

98
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,656
So the tricks he plays on you
in the future

99
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,880
