106
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,400
Since we're partners now,

107
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:35,080
you can't hide your actions
from me anymore.

108
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,320
Ever since the day
I entered the Song family,

109
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,056
