110
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,520
every minute.

111
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,216
But when have they ever succeeded?

112
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,696
Besides,

113
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,160
the best defense is a good offense.

114
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,480
I'll never just sit back and wait for doom.

115
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,216
Something is wrong.

116
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,496
An Ning found gaps
in the company's accounts.

117
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,320
A ten-billion debt
can't be hidden anymore.

118
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,896
She's on her way here to demand answers.

119
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,656
She and Huo Xiao have teamed up,

120
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,320
