121
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:10,480
Then don't blame me for being ruthless.

122
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,680
[Personal Financial Statement]

123
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:18,376
You've heard about
the company's massive debt, right?

124
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,560
Good timing.

125
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,256
I was about to look for you

126
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,816
to talk about this matter.

127
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:26,216
No idea who leaked the news.

128
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,696
But now there are many rumors outside

129
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,776
about the company going bankrupt.

130
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,016
If we don't fix this

131
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,736
before the Stock Market opens
tomorrow,

132
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:36,176
our stock price will plummet for sure.

133
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,320
It might even get delisted.

134
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,016
Whoever caused this trouble

135
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,240
should be the one to solve it.

136
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,360
That's fair enough.

137
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,217
But

138
00:06:47,241 --> 00:06:50,040
