139
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:53,640
So you have to be the one to patch it up.

140
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,616
Chairman,

141
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,216
I'm planning to expand our sales scale.

142
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,840
Resolve the debt by boosting profits.

143
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,897
Too slow.

144
00:07:08,921 --> 00:07:10,576
We can't recover cash that quickly.

145
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,656
Then let's cut costs
and improve efficiency.

146
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,377
And conduct layoffs and restructuring.

147
00:07:12,401 --> 00:07:13,560
A drop in the bucket.

148
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,817
It won't have an instant effect.

149
00:07:14,841 --> 00:07:16,696
Then let's collect
outstanding payments early.

150
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,856
That's not realistic.

151
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:18,777
Besides,

152
00:07:18,801 --> 00:07:20,600
