153
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,576
You all can head back for now.

154
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,936
Let me think about it.

155
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,240
Okay, Chairman.

156
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,297
Chairman,

157
00:07:31,321 --> 00:07:32,520
I might have an idea.

158
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,817
This is Vincent.

159
00:07:33,841 --> 00:07:36,456
A legendary and mysterious big shot
in the investment field.

160
