perhaps only he can save the group.

161
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,560
[Vincent]

162
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,200
How did you hear about this guy?

163
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,936
Isn't there some theory that says,

164
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,056
through just five people,

165
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,400
you can be connected to anyone?

166
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,880
I asked around through a friend too.

167
00:07:57,520 --> 00:08:00,080
At this point, it's all or nothing.

168
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,496
Set up a meeting with him
as soon as possible.

169
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,520
Alright.

170
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,296
Hope this Vincent.

171
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,976
[Vincent] can really turn things around

172
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,200
as the rumors say.

173
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,640
[Vincent]

174
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,336
Tomorrow night at eight.

175
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,776
Meet me at Twin Star Hotel.

176
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,240
We'll go over the details in person.

177
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,360
What's with this Vincent?

178
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:41,176
[Clarke Ventures Ltd]

179
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,937
Wait...

180
00:08:41,961 --> 00:08:44,176
Does he mistake me for some loose woman?

181
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,000
Thinking I'd trade myself
for an investment?

182
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,257
- Hey girl.
- What are you doing?

183
00:08:54,281 --> 00:08:55,336
You've got quite a stunning figure.

184
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,760
Come upstairs and hang out with me.

185
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,760
Don't do that, keep it decent.

186
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,080
Hit him!

187
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:02,320
That's what you get for stepping in.

188
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,840
Aren't you guys going to stop them?

189
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,016
There's no stopping him.

190
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,696
He's the former owner of this hotel.

191
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,296
Also a well-known local ruffian.

192
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,056
Now the hotel's been taken over
by Vincent.

193
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,096
He just can't accept that.

194
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,816
So he comes here every day,
causing scenes and driving guests away.

195
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,056
Like a stubborn shadow
that won't go away.

196
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,760
And we can't get rid of him
no matter what.

197
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,360
Hit him!

198
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,400
Hit!

199
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,600
I only invest in people.

200
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,096
Show me you've got
what it takes to impress me.

201
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,976
This hotel is one I acquired.

202
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,216
You probably understand
the current situation.

203
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,440
How you solve this nuisance

204
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,696
is my test for you.

205
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,560
Remember to keep it
on speaker the whole time.

206
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,936
You can head back first.

207
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,960
I'll handle this.

208
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,880
So you're the former owner of this hotel?

209
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,577
Girl,

210
00:10:22,601 --> 00:10:24,320
you came to see me for something?

211
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,320
Smells good.

212
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,776
As long as you please me a little,

213
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,080
