214
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,296
You dare hit me?

215
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,880
Watch your mouth.

216
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,856
I'm here to talk about the hotel business.

217
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,840
Not to deal with
your shameless behavior.

218
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,576
Listen,

219
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,096
I'm staying at this hotel for the New Year.

220
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,017
And as for you,

221
00:10:54,041 --> 00:10:55,656
don't even think about

222
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,040
leaving this room easily today!

223
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,760
So there's no room for discussion?

224
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,520
If you spend the night with me,

225
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,416
we can negotiate.

226
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,816
A woman like you with such charm

227
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,616
is the most alluring kind.

228
00:11:08,617 --> 00:11:19,617
Officail Website : dramacool.club  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

229
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,760
Just help me relax,

230
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,320
