231
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,040
Do you really think that's possible?

232
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:18,160
Just one look from you
makes me feel filthy.

233
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,720
You shameless thing!

234
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,680
You've got quite a sharp tongue, huh.

235
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,776
Seems I'll have to strip you naked,

236
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,497
string you up and make you suffer.

237
00:11:24,521 --> 00:11:26,056
Make you get on your knees
and beg like a dog.

238
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:28,360
Let's see if Vincent
dares to show up then!

239
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,560
Oops, that shot went off.

240
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,216
What about the next one?

241
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:41,096
Will you be lucky again?

242
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,320
Guess you've got some guts.

243
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,536
Just you wait, come on!

244
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:47,160
I don't want to hear another word
from you.

245
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,176
Keep your mouth shut.

246
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,800
If that gun slips out,

247
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,440
