248
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:55,416
Heard you made some money
selling that hotel.

249
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:57,376
And now
you're using this hooligan method

250
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:59,600
to make Vincent sell it back to you
at a low price.

251
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:02,680
Bought low, sold high, played both sides.

252
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,840
You really have a dark heart.

253
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,536
I was wrong, please don't...

254
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,840
Please don't.

255
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,680
You've got two options now.

256
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,320
Either

257
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,816
I end you right here,

258
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,360
and they carry you out flat.

259
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,176
Or

260
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,440
I give you
one percent of the hotel shares.

261
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:21,176
If you manage it well,

262
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,256
I can

263
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,600
offer you extra shares
as a bonus every year.

264
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,920
I... I want the shares.

265
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,896
But your words don't mean much
without proof.

266
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,040
I've never even met him.

267
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,240
How do I know you're not tricking me?

268
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,616
Looks like I finally got my chance.

269
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,696
I'll beat you to a pulp!

270
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,760
Where's that arrogance
from a minute ago?

271
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,120
We finally meet.

272
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,760
Vincent.

273
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:21,950
