through cracks of darkness ♪

275
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:29,450
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

276
00:13:32,990 --> 00:13:36,250
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

277
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:39,810
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

278
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:43,380
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

279
00:13:45,690 --> 00:13:52,760
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

280
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:56,796
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

281
00:13:56,820 --> 00:14:00,396
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

282
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:03,356
♪ Burn like fire ♪

283
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:06,800
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

284
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:10,890
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

285
00:14:10,940 --> 00:14:13,626
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

286
00:14:13,650 --> 00:14:16,790
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

287
00:14:17,070 --> 00:14:20,570
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

288
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:27,100
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

289
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:31,076
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

290
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:34,620
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

291
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:41,370
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

292
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:43,630
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

